					    <h1>
                            Pay no attention to the dead teenager: Ferguson Police tries to shift the blame in Michael Brown shooting                        </h1>

					    <h2>
                            Police Chief Tom Jackson addresses Michael Brown -- and attempts to shift blame in his shooting                        </h2>

					    <span class="byline"><a href='http://www.salon.com/writer/joanna_rothkopf/' rel='author' class="gaTrackLinkEvent" data-ga-track-json="[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;click&quot;, &quot;Joanna Rothkopf&quot;]" >Joanna Rothkopf</a></span>

                        
